---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SchemaMarkup from '../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro';

const draft = false;
const publishDate = "April 1, 2026";
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "8 min read";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="How We Built a $250K Cleaning Business From the Couch"
  description="The real story of how Todd and Christen built The Valley Clean Team from $0 to $250K after a broken leg and a surprise layoff. Inspiration for local entrepreneurs."
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="How We Built a $250,000 Cleaning Business From the Couch"
    description="The real story of how Todd and Christen built The Valley Clean Team from $0 to $250K after a broken leg and a surprise layoff. Inspiration for local entrepreneurs."
    publishDate={publishDate}
    author={author}
  />
  

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Our Journey
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          How We Built a $250,000 Business<br>
          <span class="text-[#FFA985]">From the Couch</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>{publishDate}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <article class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">

        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Have you ever felt like the universe was trying to tell you something — loudly? In August 2022, Todd was airlifted from our land after breaking his leg so holiday he couldn't walk for five months. We had a 10-month-old baby, a new move that wasn’t even unpacked, and zero weight-bearing on his leg.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          Then, in October, I (Christen) was surprise-laid off from my corporate marketing job. Zero income. A broken leg. A baby. Most people would call that a disaster. We called it our "forced to start."
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">The "Boring" Business Pivot</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          While Todd was stuck on the couch with a remote and his brain, he found a YouTube video talking about "boring businesses." He realized that while tech startups grab the headlines, the local economies in North Alabama are built on things like cleaning, plumbing, and landscaping.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          We didn't have a bank loan. We didn't have investors. We had less than $5,000 and the will to survive. We realized that if we could provide a service that was reliable, professional, and actually cared about the people doing the work, we could build something special.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">From $0 to $250,000</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          In just one year, we've scaled to a team of 13 providers and are projecting $250,000 in revenue for our first full calendar year. We didn't do it with fancy tech — we did it with:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600">
          <li><strong>Low-Cost Tools:</strong> Using BookingKoala for scheduling and Canva for our branding.</li>
          <li><strong>Extreme People-Focus:</strong> Paying our providers more than the industry standard (our 50/50 split).</li>
          <li><strong>Relentless Honesty:</strong> Admitting when we're wrong and fixing it immediately.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          If you’re waiting for the "perfect time" to start your dream, look at us. We built the airplane while we were flying it. We started with nothing but a broken leg and a vision of what a cleaning company *should* look like.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          Today, we serve hundreds of families across Huntsville, Nashville, and beyond. We aren't just cleaning houses; we're giving people back their weekends and proving that you don't need a corporate office to build a high-impact business.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">What's Next for TVCT?</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          We're just getting started. Our goal is to continue growing our provider network and expanding our reach into more communities. We want to be the name you trust when you need your home refreshed, and the name cleaners want to work with because we treat them with the respect they deserve.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8 italic">
          If we can build a $250k business from a couch, imagine what you can do.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Ready to Get Your Time Back?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join the hundreds of families who trust The Valley Clean Team. Get an instant quote and book your first clean in 60 seconds.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="tel:256-826-1100" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gray-900 text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors text-lg">
          Call 256-826-1100
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-gray-900 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-lg">
          Get a Free Quote
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
